ntribute to the movement.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://justicedemocrats.com/volunteer-skills/\">Tell us how you can help</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe8CfK0gUULEVpYFm9Eb4iyGOL-_iDl395qB0z4hny7ek4iNw/viewform\">Tell us about your congressional district</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSceYguZI_gngXf7dLOXN6xUkLRNsYfn0b2v-aDEvZKPH-j1dQ/viewform\">Connect us with people we should talk to</a></li>\r\n        <li>Research to find candidates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),(553,133,'_sections_1_content','field_58858c11fcec7'),(554,133,'sections_2_content','We just witnessed two impossible things happen. One, Donald Trump is POTUS. Two, a little known socialist from Vermont launched an issue driven campaign and nearly defeated the most powerful political machine in America. \r\n\r\nPolitically, all bets are off, but we do have a choice. We can go down with the ship in a blaze of fascist glory or correct our course as a nation. We have everything we need to build a thriving economy, give everyone a good education and healthcare, massively reduce our prison population, and become a world-renowned democracy again. The one key ingredient we are missing is a government that represents the people of this country. So let\'s change that. We are going to recruit hundreds of Justice Democrats to run the biggest campaign this country has ever seen, and we\'re going to replace every politician in Congress that puts the needs of corporate donors above people.'),(555,133,'_sections_2_content','field_587cda9f44136'),(556,133,'sections_3_shortcode','[custom-facebook-feed]'),(557,133,'_sections_3_shortcode','field_587cdb024413d'),(558,133,'sections','a:4:{i:0;s:5:\"video\";i:1;s:7:\"act_now\";i:2;s:15:\"general_content\";i:3;s:9:\"shortcode\";}'),(559,133,'_sections','field_587cda7c44134'),(560,2,'sections_1_content','We are recruiting Justice Democrats to run a unified campaign to replace every establishment p